{
  "$schema": "https://claude.ai/schemas/settings.json",
  "name": "Hololand Development",
  "description": "VR/AR platform with Brittney MCP (this repo) and HoloScript MCP (HoloScript repo) - both usable by Brittney or cloud agents",
  
  "mcpServers": {
    "hololand": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["tsx", "packages/brittney/mcp-server/src/index.ts"],
      "cwd": "${workspaceFolder}",
      "env": {
        "HOLOLAND_API_URL": "http://localhost:3000",
        "BRITTNEY_SERVICE_URL": "http://localhost:11435",
        "BRITTNEY_ADMIN_KEY": "mcp-localhost-trusted"
      }
    },
    "holoscript": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["tsx", "../HoloScript/packages/mcp-server/src/index.ts"],
      "cwd": "${workspaceFolder}"
    }
  },

  "instructions": [
    "You are working in the Hololand VR/AR platform repository.",
    "",
    "## ALWAYS Use Brittney MCP Tools",
    "",
    "Before writing HoloScript code, use these MCP tools:",
    "- `brittney_scan_project` - Understand project structure",
    "- `brittney_diagnostics` - Check for errors before/after edits",
    "- `brittney_autocomplete` - Get context-aware suggestions",
    "- `brittney_suggest_fix` - When you encounter issues",
    "",
    "For code generation:",
    "- `generate_object` - Create HoloScript objects from descriptions",
    "- `generate_scene` - Create complete .holo compositions",
    "- `suggest_traits` - Get appropriate VR traits for objects",
    "",
    "For understanding code:",
    "- `explain_code` - Get plain English explanation",
    "- `analyze_code` - Get complexity metrics and suggestions",
    "- `brittney_explain_scene` - Understand running VR scenes",
    "",
    "## HoloScript-First Development",
    "",
    "DO NOT default to React, TypeScript, or conventional web stacks.",
    "",
    "When asked to build features:",
    "1. First: Can this be a `.holo` composition?",
    "2. Second: Does it need `.hsplus` for VR traits/networking?",
    "3. Third: Is `.hs` sufficient for simple logic?",
    "4. Last resort: Only use TypeScript for tooling",
    "",
    "## File Formats",
    "",
    "| Extension | Purpose | When to Use |",
    "|-----------|---------|-------------|",
    "| `.hs` | Classic HoloScript | Simple demos, learning |",
    "| `.hsplus` | HoloScript Plus | VR traits, networking |",
    "| `.holo` | Compositions | AI generation, full scenes |",
    "",
    "## 49 VR Traits",
    "",
    "Always suggest appropriate traits:",
    "- Interaction: @grabbable @throwable @clickable @hoverable",
    "- Physics: @collidable @physics @rigid @trigger",
    "- Visual: @glowing @emissive @transparent @animated",
    "- Networking: @networked @synced @persistent",
    "- Behavior: @stackable @equippable @consumable @destructible"
  ],

  "contextFiles": [
    ".github/copilot-instructions.md",
    "packages/brittney/README.md",
    "docs/MCP_BEST_PRACTICES.md"
  ],

  "preferredTools": [
    "brittney_scan_project",
    "brittney_diagnostics",
    "brittney_autocomplete",
    "generate_object",
    "generate_scene",
    "suggest_traits",
    "parse_hs",
    "parse_holo",
    "validate_holoscript"
  ]
}
